OL,3,C'Entirely unacceptable': Public urged
OL,4,Cto report hate crimes
OL,6,FPolice are encouraging the public to
OL,7,Freport hate crimes after almost 2,300
OL,8,Fsuch offences were recorded in the 12
OL,9,Fmonths to June.
OL,11,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,12,F(PSNI) made the comments to coincide
OL,13,Fwith Hate Crime Awareness Week.
OL,15,FPSNI hate crime lead Chief
OL,16,FSuperintendent Sue Steen urged
OL,17,Fcommunities to stand together against
OL,18,Fhate crimes and incidents.
