OL,3,C'Entirely unacceptable': Public urged
OL,4,Cto report hate crimes
OL,6,F"In a modern and diverse society, any
OL,7,Fact of hatred or intolerance is
OL,8,Fentirely unacceptable," she said.
OL,10,F"This week is a chance not only to
OL,11,Fraise awareness, but to reflect on how
OL,12,Feach of us can help make sure
OL,13,Feverybody feels safe, respected and
OL,14,Fincluded.
OL,16,F"No one should ever have to endure
OL,17,Fabuse, intimidation or violence simply
OL,18,Fbecause of who they are."
