OL,3,C'Entirely unacceptable': Public urged
OL,4,Cto report hate crimes
OL,6,FShe said there was a person or a
OL,7,Ffamily behind the 2,300 hate crimes
OL,8,Frecorded as of June 30.
OL,10,F"But we believe many more go
OL,11,Funreported and without reporting, we
OL,12,Fcannot support victims, detect
OL,13,Fpatterns, allocate resources, or bring
OL,14,Fperpetrators to justice," she said.
