OL,3,C'Entirely unacceptable': Public urged
OL,4,Cto report hate crimes
OL,6,F"This week I want to encourage people
OL,7,Fwho witness or experience hate-
OL,8,Fmotivated abuse, harassment or
OL,9,Fcriminal damage, to please report it
OL,10,Fto police via 101 (or 999 in an
OL,11,Femergency) or online via the PSNI
OL,12,Fwebsite.
OL,14,F"Hate crime reports receive enhanced
OL,15,Foversight, daily review and, where
OL,16,Fpossible, dedicated problem-solving by
OL,17,Fneighbourhood policing teams.
