OL,3,C'Entirely unacceptable': Public urged
OL,4,Cto report hate crimes
OL,6,F"HCAS offers a safe and confidential
OL,7,Fspace to provide support to victims of
OL,8,Fhate crimes across the different
OL,9,Fprotected characteristics. They can
OL,10,Fsupport you whether or not you have
OL,11,Freported the crime to the police.
OL,13,F"Every person in Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fdeserves to live without fear or
OL,15,Fintimidation.
